query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS work_logs (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  employeeId INT NOT NULL,
  machineId INT,
  workType ENUM('maintenance', 'refill', 'cleaning', 'repair', 'inspection', 'installation', 'other') NOT NULL,
  status ENUM('in_progress', 'completed', 'cancelled') DEFAULT 'in_progress' NOT NULL,
  startTime TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  endTime TIMESTAMP NULL,
  duration INT,
  description TEXT,
  notes TEXT,
  issuesFound TEXT,
  partsUsed TEXT,
  photoUrls TEXT,
  rating INT,
  verifiedBy INT,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
